684
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:54,671
Must we live like a marble
In a soda's spin?

685
00:43:55,713 --> 00:43:58,880
Trapped with no escape
No light within

686
00:43:58,963 --> 00:44:03,421
Want to feel high?
Skip the liquor's sway

687
00:44:04,546 --> 00:44:07,463
Play the beat
Drop the music, watch them pay

688
00:44:07,546 --> 00:44:10,380
Your heart's the rhythm
Your steps the beat

689
